#ident	"@(#)nadmin.nfs:setup/nfs/Help	1.1"
share:TITLE:Shares a Local Resource Automatically-Immediately via NFS
mount:TITLE:Mounts a Remote Resource Automatically-Immediately via NFS

setup:share:
	The nfs_share task allows you to make
	local resources available to remote systems
	via the Network File System.  You may set 
	up automatic sharing, share resources 
	immediately, or both.

setup:mount:
	The nfs_mount task allows you to make remote
	resources available ato your local users via
	Network File system.  You may set up automatic
	mounting, mount resources imediately, or both.
